data.description:
Welcome to Highline at Redpoint Square in the Summerlin Masterplan community with easy access to Downtown Summerlin, Red Rock Canyon, Summerlin Ballpark & more! This new townhome, complete with an ELEVATOR, offers a perfect blend of luxury and modern convenience. The gated community offers many amenities including a community pool, playground and gathering areas.

Inside, you'll discover all-new appliances, including a washer and dryer. The property also features a fully paid-off reverse osmosis system, water softner and a Ring alarm system for added security. Featuring sleek white cabinets, Calacatta Lasa Quartz countertops, and a mix of ceramic tile, vinyl plank flooring, and plush carpet. Stainless steel kitchen appliances, USB outlets in the kitchen and master. Open up the sliding glass door to upgraded outdoor floor covered with natural look stone pavers, and fresh clean no maintenance green synthetic turf. 
Current mortgage is ASSUMABLE!
